OL,6,FLabour MP Vicky Foxcroft has resigned
OL,7,Fas a government whip over the party's
OL,8,Fwelfare proposals, saying that she
OL,9,Fcould not vote "for reforms which
OL,10,Finclude cuts to disabled people's
OL,11,Ffinances".
OL,13,FIn a letter to Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,14,FStarmer, the MP for Lewisham North
OL,15,Fsaid: "I absolutely understand the
OL,16,Fneed to address the ever-increasing
OL,17,Fwelfare bill in these difficult
OL,18,Feconomic times.
