OL,6,FThe government's proposals ` aimed at
OL,7,Fencouraging more people off sickness
OL,8,Fbenefits and into work ` are set to
OL,9,Finclude the tightening of criteria for
OL,10,Fpersonal independence payment (Pip),
OL,11,Fwhich is the main disability benefit.
OL,13,FThey also include a cut to the
OL,14,Fsickness-related element of universal
OL,15,Fcredit (UC) and delayed access to only
OL,16,Fthose aged 22 and over.
