OL,3,CLabour whip resigns over government's
OL,4,Cproposed welfare cuts
OL,6,FMinisters are likely to face a Commons
OL,7,Fstand-off with backbench Labour MPs
OL,8,Fover their plans, with dozens of them
OL,9,Flast month saying the proposals were
OL,10,F"impossible to support".
OL,12,FThe legislation, known as the
OL,13,FUniversal Credit and Personal
OL,14,FIndependence Payment Bill, was
OL,15,Fformally introduced to the Commons on
OL,16,FWednesday. MPs will debate a second
OL,17,Freading of the bill on July 1.
